<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ArticleSwift</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/article-icon.svg" type="image/svg" />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/7f027a8137.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>ArticleSwift</h1>
      <nav class="sidebar">
        <ul>
          <li onclick="hideSidebar()"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></li>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li>
            <a href="/article/create">Create new Article</a>
          </li>
          <li><a href="/article">All Articles</a></li>
          <li>
            <button class="logoutbtn" onclick="logout()" type="submit">
              <a href="/login">Log Out</a>
            </button>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <nav class="navbar">
        <ul>
          <li class="navresp"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="navresp">
            <a href="/article/create">Create new Article</a>
          </li>
          <li class="navresp"><a href="/article">All Articles</a></li>
          <li class="navresp">
            <button class="logoutbtn" onclick="logout()" type="submit">
              <a href="/login">Log Out</a>
            </button>
          </li>
          <li onclick="showSidebar()"><i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <article class="index-art">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ex unde quidem
        nam vel modi fuga perspiciatis eveniet aut, quos, tempore non eius sed
        consequuntur debitis quaerat quod repellat excepturi libero eos esse hic
        at maxime corporis beatae. Reiciendis nesciunt quaerat deleniti a
        officia totam soluta error et asperiores! Autem porro aperiam
        reprehenderit facere et, sed, minus illo ullam adipisci dolores quidem
        impedit unde commodi qui fugiat laudantium veritatis id cupiditate
        accusamus alias, maxime temporibus aliquam. Consequuntur, fugiat quidem.
        Mollitia nihil dolorum magni maxime culpa, ratione omnis quia suscipit
        debitis! Quo, odio quam minus nemo facilis illum odit sunt neque sint.
      </p>
    </article>
    <div class="routing">
      <h1>Use the following routes:</h1>
      <p>/article/:id -> Fetch an article by its id.</p>
      <p>/article/:id/update -> Update an article by its id.</p>
      <p>/article/:id/delete -> Delete an article by its id.</p>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <p>&copy; ArticleSwift 2024</p>
      <p>Instagram | Twitter | Discord</p>
    </footer>
    <script>
      function logout() {
        fetch("/logout", {
          method: "POST",
          body: JSON.stringify({ logout: true }),
        }).catch((error) => {
          console.log(error);
        });
      }
      function showSidebar() {
        document.querySelector(".sidebar").style.display = "flex";
      }
      function hideSidebar() {
        document.querySelector(".sidebar").style.display = "none";
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
